Package: trackDJ
Title: Track Display Jockey (trackDJ): A User-friendly R Package for Visualization of Epigenomic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Neha", "Bokil", , "nbokil@alum.mit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: a programmable visualization tool for reproducible epigenomic figure generation in R. Visualize chromatin tracks across the genome. Instead of screenshotting IGV, or uploading tracks to UCSC genome browser, try this function for streamlining and beautify-ing your figures.
